---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Experience — Mike Hnath">

  <div class="section">
    <div class="page-title">Experience</div>
    <div class="body-text">I didn't stumble into different industries — I chose them. Each W2 role was a deliberate skill build: luxury retail production, licensed CPG at scale, enterprise digital shelf, B2B SaaS demand gen, regulated pharma media. Through all of it, <strong>THIS</strong> ran in the background as a side consultancy. It never stopped. In 2024, it became the full-time primary.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="section" style="padding-top:0;padding-bottom:21px;margin-top:-20px">
    <a class="resume-link" href="#" download>Download résumé</a>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div style="font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:12px;font-family:var(--font-display)">The foundation — music industry, live production, early business</div>
    <div class="foundation-card">
      <div class="foundation-desc">Before marketing was my career, music was my business. I started a band in college, booked 350+ shows across North America, grew our following to 20K organically, and landed two distribution deals and a Mesa/Boogie endorsement — all self-managed, no label, no safety net. When the chance came to tour-manage Within the Ruins across 22 countries through eOne Music, I said yes and figured out international logistics, visa paperwork, and border crossings on the fly.
        <br><br>
        That period taught me something no degree could: when you're the only one responsible for the outcome, you learn fast or you fail publicly.</div>
      <div class="foundation-grid">
        <div class="foundation-bullets">
          <div class="foundation-bullet"><div class="foundation-dot"></div><div>Founded DID Entertainment at 17 — 501(c)(3) concert production, 12–14 events end-to-end</div></div>
          <div class="foundation-bullet"><div class="foundation-dot"></div><div>Founded Ark of the Covenant — 350+ shows, 2 distribution deals, 20K+ followers, 100K+ streams</div></div>
          <div class="foundation-bullet"><div class="foundation-dot"></div><div>Tour manager for Within the Ruins — 250+ shows, 22 countries, $120K+ merch revenue</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="foundation-bullets">
          <div class="foundation-bullet"><div class="foundation-dot"></div><div>Freelance audio engineer at Webster Theater — 1,500-capacity venue, 3 years</div></div>
          <div class="foundation-bullet"><div class="foundation-dot"></div><div>A.S. in Small Business Management — earned while actively running DID</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-label" style="margin-bottom:0">Featured case studies</div>
      <a class="show-more" href="/Personal/case-studies/" style="margin-top:0">View all</a>
    </div>
    <div id="experience-work"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="section" style="padding-top:25px">
    <div class="section-label">Career</div>
    <div class="tl-row"><div class="tl-year">2024–now</div><div class="tl-dot-col"><div class="tl-dot"></div><div class="tl-line"></div></div><div class="tl-body"><div class="tl-role">Owner — THIS (full-time)</div><div class="tl-co">Brand strategy · Creative direction · GTM consulting</div><div class="tl-tags"><span class="tl-tag">Brand</span><span class="tl-tag">GTM</span><span class="tl-tag">Packaging</span></div></div></div>
    <div class="tl-row"><div class="tl-year">2022–2024</div><div class="tl-dot-col"><div class="tl-dot"></div><div class="tl-line"></div></div><div class="tl-body"><div class="tl-role">Digital Marketing Manager — POCN</div><div class="tl-co">Pharma paid media · $1.7M+ managed · J&amp;J, Lilly, AbbVie, Regeneron</div><div class="tl-tags"><span class="tl-tag">Performance</span><span class="tl-tag">Healthcare</span></div></div></div>
    <div class="tl-row"><div class="tl-year">2021–2022</div><div class="tl-dot-col"><div class="tl-dot"></div><div class="tl-line"></div></div><div class="tl-body"><div class="tl-role">Marketing Content Manager — Triax Technologies</div><div class="tl-co">B2B SaaS · Enterprise demand gen · Fortune 50 pipeline</div><div class="tl-tags"><span class="tl-tag">B2B SaaS</span><span class="tl-tag">GTM</span></div></div></div>
    <div class="tl-row"><div class="tl-year">2020–2021</div><div class="tl-dot-col"><div class="tl-dot"></div><div class="tl-line"></div></div><div class="tl-body"><div class="tl-role">Art Director — Imaginary Content (Kraft Heinz)</div><div class="tl-co">Digital shelf · eComm · 800+ assets · ~30 brands</div><div class="tl-tags"><span class="tl-tag">CPG</span><span class="tl-tag">Design</span></div></div></div>
    <div class="tl-row"><div class="tl-year">2018–2019</div><div class="tl-dot-col"><div class="tl-dot"></div><div class="tl-line"></div></div><div class="tl-body"><div class="tl-role">Creative Director — Infinity Lifestyle Brands</div><div class="tl-co">Licensed CPG · $10M+ licensing · Disney, MLBPA, Viacom</div><div class="tl-tags"><span class="tl-tag">Brand</span><span class="tl-tag">Licensing</span></div></div></div>
    <div class="tl-row"><div class="tl-year">2017–2018</div><div class="tl-dot-col"><div class="tl-dot"></div><div class="tl-line"></div></div><div class="tl-body"><div class="tl-role">Graphic and Production Designer — Mitchells Stores</div><div class="tl-co">Luxury retail · $6K in 3 days from digital magalogue</div><div class="tl-tags"><span class="tl-tag">Design</span><span class="tl-tag">Retail</span></div></div></div>
    <div class="tl-row"><div class="tl-year">2008–2016</div><div class="tl-dot-col"><div class="tl-dot"></div></div><div class="tl-body"><div class="tl-role">The foundation</div><div class="tl-co">Music industry · Live production · Early business building</div><div class="tl-tags"><span class="tl-tag">Founder</span><span class="tl-tag">Touring</span><span class="tl-tag">Production</span></div><div class="tl-note">Full detail above</div></div></div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-label">Core skills</div>
    <div class="skills-grid">
      <div>
        <div class="skill-col-title">Strategy</div>
        <div class="skill-chips">
          <span class="chip expert">Brand strategy</span><span class="chip expert">GTM planning</span>
          <span class="chip expert">Positioning</span><span class="chip expert">Product commercialization</span>
          <span class="chip">Sales enablement</span><span class="chip">Market research</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="skill-col-title">Performance</div>
        <div class="skill-chips">
          <span class="chip expert">Meta Ads</span><span class="chip expert">LinkedIn Ads</span>
          <span class="chip expert">Programmatic</span><span class="chip expert">Media planning</span>
          <span class="chip expert">Campaign optimization</span><span class="chip">SEO</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="skill-col-title">Creative</div>
        <div class="skill-chips">
          <span class="chip expert">Creative direction</span><span class="chip expert">Packaging design</span>
          <span class="chip expert">Art direction</span><span class="chip expert">UX/UI</span>
          <span class="chip expert">Figma</span><span class="chip expert">Adobe Suite</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div style="margin-top:20px">
      <a class="btn resume-link" href="/Personal/tools/">View tools and stack</a>
    </div>
  </div>

</Base>
